` accepted a list?","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/comments/735942485","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich/issues/458#issuecomment-735942485","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/458","id":735942485,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDczNTk0MjQ4NQ==","user":{"login":"bradh11","id":18483910,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4NDgzOTEw","avatar_url":"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/18483910?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11","html_url":"https://github.com/bradh11","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bradh11/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-11-30T17:53:32Z","updated_at":"2020-11-30T17:53:32Z","author_association":"NONE","body":"Well that actually seems to be the trick.  We tried using Rich with a servicenow integration we are doing and hit a roadblock and needed to switch to PrettyTable library because of this issue.  \r\n\r\nThanks much,\r\nBrad\r\n\r\n```\r\nfrom snow import Snow\r\nfrom prettytable import PrettyTable\r\nfrom tables import *\r\nimport yaml\r\nfrom pprint import pprint\r\n\r\ndev_tab = PrettyTable()\r\nloc_tab = PrettyTable()\r\nuser_tab = PrettyTable()\r\n\r\nwith open('config.yaml', 'r') as cf:\r\n    conf = yaml.safe_load(cf)\r\n\r\ndev_tab.field_names = device_columns\r\nloc_tab.field_names = location_columns\r\nuser_tab.field_names = users_columns\r\n\r\nc = Snow(instance=conf['INSTANCE'], company_id='LIONS001', username=conf['USERNAME'], password=conf['PASSWORD'])\r\n\r\ndevices = c.get_devices()\r\nlocations = c.get_locations()\r\nusers = c.get_users()\r\n\r\nfor x in devices:\r\n    row = [x.get(col) for col in device_columns]\r\n    dev_tab.add_row(row)\r\n\r\nfor x in locations:\r\n    row = [x.get(col) for col in location_columns]\r\n    loc_tab.add_row(row)\r\n\r\nfor x in users:\r\n    row = [x.get(col) for col in users_columns]\r\n    user_tab.add_row(row)\r\n\r\nprint(dev_tab)\r\nprint(loc_tab)\r\nprint(user_tab)\r\n\r\n```","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/comments/735948901","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich/issues/458#issuecomment-735948901","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/willmcgugan/rich/issues/458","id":735948901,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDczNTk0ODkwMQ==","user":{"login":"willmcgugan","id":554369,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU1NDM2OQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/554369?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan","html_url":"https://github.com/willmcgugan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/willmcgugan/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2020-11-30T18:05:18Z","updated_at":"2020-11-30T18:05:18Z","author_association":"OWNER","